\nc<Nika>If I head East I can get to Janlen Village.
From there I should be able to find passage on a
ship to get to the Gognan Isles.
\nc<Emily>Who are you and what do you want?
\nc<Molderan Mage>You see there was someone very dear to
me that was taken from me. \!His name was Arnold. My
brother and I were very close.
\nc<Molderan Mage>Yes. You see, I inquired about his death
once I heard of it. One can only imagine  how utterly
upset I would be when I found out how he was killed in an
old Elven cave while being accompanied by an Elven girl.
\nc<Molderan Mage>Of course, the Elven girl survived somehow.
\nc<Nika>There's nothing I can do to bring your brother
back. But I did nothing to sabotage our mission and I
was loyal to him to the very end.
\nc<Molderan Mage>Then why not report back?! Why are you
\nc<Nika>Because I no longer follow that path...
\nc<Molderan Mage>Silly girl. You belong to the Molderan
Army now. You will do as you're told.
\nc<Nika>Listen. I don't want to fight you but if you
insist, let's get this over with. I have more important
Elven whore! I may have lost this fight but know that
I will come back for revenge!
\nc<Emily>She definitely has it in for you...\!we can
be sure that we'll see her again in the future...
\nc<Nika>...I guess I have no choice but to be ready for
when she shows up next then...
\nc<Emily>Let's head back to Regulus and tell him what
